    public abstract class MiddleCommandType
extends CRCLCommandType
    The abstract MiddleCommandType is derived from CRCLCommandType. MiddleCommandType has the following elements: Name (inherited, optional) CommandID (inherited). MiddleCommandType is the abstract parent type of specific CRCL command types. Only derived types of MiddleCommandType may be instantiated.
